    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>B)</strong> <strong style="margin-left:15px;">PLUMBING:</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Checking motor and pumps running condition</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Filling water in all water tanks and sumps</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Checking plumbing lines</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >All motor and pump maintenance</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Common area water supply line checking</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">f) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Sewage line checking</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">g) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Periodic check plumbing assets</span></p>
    
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>C)</strong> <strong style="margin-left:15px;">ELECTRICAL:</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Lighting switch off and on schedules</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Checking all common area lighting</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Meter panel checking</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >DG operation</span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Periodic checking of electrical assets</span></p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>D)</strong> <strong style="margin-left:15px;">GARDENING: :</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Daily watering of all plants </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Monthly trimming </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Monthly loosening the soil </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Maneuvering and adding fertilizers as and when necessary</span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Periodical pesticide spray treatment </span></p>
    
    
    
    
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>F)</strong> <strong style="margin-left:15px;">SECURITY SERVICE:  </strong>
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >To monitor the vehicle movement </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >To monitor material movement </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Maintaining visitor's pass</span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Having a check on the unknown visitors </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Patrolling </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">f) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Regular checks during the night   </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">g) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Monitoring on the service providers - Drivers and others </span> </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>E)</strong> <strong style="margin-left:15px;">Other maintenance scopes:
        </strong>
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Lift AMC and spare changing </span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >DG AMC, oil service and spare change </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >STP operation and maintenance  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Fused light changing  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Plumbing fittings change  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">f) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Club house maintenance   </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">g) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Fire equipment maintenance and fire extinguisher refilling</span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">h) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Common amenities maintenance   </span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">i) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >CCTV maintenance  </span>   </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:12px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">
        <strong>TERMS</strong> 
        
    </p>
    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">a) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >All activities mentioned above is only for the existing common area maintenance only not inside the flat.  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">b) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Any other activities beyond the scope of the agreement shall be estimated with 10% overheads &amp; charged as per actuals.  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">c) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >The cost incurred for the purchase of water is not in the scope of this agreement. It will be organized by the Service Provider as per actual cost.   </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">d) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >The cost incurred in bailing out sewage shall be that of the Association. However, all necessary assistance shall be provided by the service provider.  </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">e) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Replacement of dead plants or fixing new plants will not be under the scope of service provider.    </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">f) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >In case of scaffoldings are required it will be charged as per actual    </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">g) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Electrical / Plumbing equipment &amp; fitting replacement if damaged or not serviceable, is not in the scope of this agreement. </span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">h) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >All cleaning mentioned above is applicable for accessible areas only.    </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">i) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Common electricity bill will be paid up to limit of Rs. 1.2 lac per month only. Diesel limit shall be up to Rs. 25,000/- per month only.</span>  </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">j) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" > Civil works not covered in the scope</span>  </p>    
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">k) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Any government tax or any other payment not under the scope   </span> </p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">l) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Any Asset replacement is not in scope of the service provider.    </span></p>
    <p style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px; margin:2px 0;">m) <span style="text-align:left; font-size:10px; padding-left:20px;" >Any damage happened due to natural calamities is not in scope of the service provider.    </span></p>
    
    
    
